    "description": "<strong>OVERGUN</strong> is a fast-paced one-man sci-fi first-person shooter inspired by old school shooter design with modern gameplay and graphics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/447326732071e27f4f84b39dd203f3f6.poster.avif?t=1743539222\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/447326732071e27f4f84b39dd203f3f6.webm?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/447326732071e27f4f84b39dd203f3f6.mp4?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLOT</h2>Try yourself in the role of an elite class OVERGUN mercenary who will have to deal with the crazed robots of the EARTH ROBOTICS corporation. As a result of experiments on artificial intelligence, it goes out of control and turns the lunar base into a robot production factory. You have to solve this problem and destroy the army of robots on your way, and also find out what EARTH ROBOTICS was really doing.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/cb3d666999de633766f9b19aa874524f.poster.avif?t=1743539222\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/cb3d666999de633766f9b19aa874524f.webm?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/cb3d666999de633766f9b19aa874524f.mp4?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DYNAMIC FIGHTS</h2>Fast gameplay, well-designed weapons and shooting.<br>You can run along walls, overcoming obstacle after obstacle and destroying robots with maximum efficiency.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/8692188608151eba44507fd7f32526f5.poster.avif?t=1743539222\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/8692188608151eba44507fd7f32526f5.webm?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/8692188608151eba44507fd7f32526f5.mp4?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WEAPON AND CHARACTER UPGRADES</h2>At your disposal is an arsenal of 6 guns with alternative fire modes.<br>Modify your weapons and character to find the most effective way to destroy robots<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/52dcd224f00d5e9e73ef473fa9067f50.poster.avif?t=1743539222\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/52dcd224f00d5e9e73ef473fa9067f50.webm?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1890700/extras/52dcd224f00d5e9e73ef473fa9067f50.mp4?t=1743539222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
